I N S T A N C E  G E N E R A T I O N

 This section generates blades of grass using a simple bezier curve generator.  The For-Each loop enables random generation of any number
 of unique instances to be fed into the point-instancer.

S C A T T E R I N G

 Point scattering including optional scatter point display

I N S T A N C I N G

 Create and bake instance geometry or strands

A D J U S T M E N T  &  W I N D
 Adjust the stiffness property (point_ratio) on the strands and meshes, create and apply the wind field, with custom settings.
 Color can also be set here.  Wind field is generated and applied here too.

D U M M Y  S E T T I N G S

 This is the geo to scatter on and the density of the scatter.
 Feel free to plug in your own here.
